{"title":"有一片庄稼等待收割","authors":["马志刚"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":5,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一片庄稼等待收割"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马志刚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山里山外泛着汗浸透的秋色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高粱地远远地红了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉米地远远地黄了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待使人们认识了焦渴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一片庄稼熟了，知道吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一片希望熟了，知道吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知道了正在演化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"演化成秋后的晚景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一片庄稼等待收割"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风在眼前努力导演"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄的时节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假若谁是收割者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁就是播种者"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}